    "description": "THE WHY HOW DO COMPANY, Inc. provides services and solutions for smartphones in Japan. It develops platform solutions for smartphones and IoT related solutions; and handles social games and app-related services, and other contract development projects. It also operates a real estate sublease store in the Tokyo metropolitan area; and provides training for job seekers. In addition, the company engages in the music production and concert activities; planning, production, and performance of various events, including plays, entertainment shows, lectures, and sports; and management, licensing, and sale of intellectual property rights. The company was formerly known as Acrodea, Inc. and changed its name to THE WHY HOW DO COMPANY, Inc. in January 2022. THE WHY HOW DO COMPANY, Inc. was incorporated in 2004 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan."
